At the center of the Android@Home architecture

00:43:31.440 --> 00:43:37.549
is your Android device. We're extending the
Android OS to include new services that allow

00:43:37.549 --> 00:43:44.369
Android apps to discover, connect, and communicate
with appliances and devices in the home. We

00:43:44.369 --> 00:43:51.150
call this the Android@Home Framework.
