00:43:51.150 --> 00:43:56.729
we've designed an open, wireless protocol
that allows Android devices to talk to them.

00:43:56.729 --> 00:44:02.069
This new protocol enables very low-cost connectivity
with anything that's electrical in your home,

00:44:02.069 --> 00:44:08.099
such as lights, alarm clocks, thermostats,
dishwashers, et cetera.

00:44:08.099 --> 00:44:12.710
We want to think of every appliance in your
home as a potential I/O device for Android

00:44:12.710 --> 00:44:15.190
apps.
